room_title: Escape room "The Alchemy Lab" by ClueMasters Escape Room in Fort Smith
room_address: 115 North 10th Street, Suite A Fort Smith, AR 72901
room_description: You are apprentices of the recently deceased alchemist Dolores Belmont. In her will, she left you a treasure that could grant you eternal life: The Philosopher's Stone! But you only have one hour to uncover her secrets before the unstable chemicals in her lab explode!
